<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-06 02:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4778 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BKN-NBANOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      06-06 1874
