<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-06 02:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4784 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HKN-NHLNOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      06-06 1769
