<HEADLINE>
DIVIDEND MEETINGS 
</HEADLINE>
  (lb) 
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Following is a partial list of dividend meetings for this week:
</P>
<P>
   MONDAY
</P>
<P>
   Agree Rlty
</P>
<P>
   Central Vt Pub Svc
</P>
