<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-06 17:26 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4914 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  AM-PAGE1-CONSIDER-NYT     06-06 0510
</HEADER>
<BODY>
 AM-PAGE1-CONSIDER-NYT 
 (HLW)
<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the stories that New York Times editors are considering
for Page 1, Monday, June 7. The N.Y. Times News Service late-night
supervisor will be Sam Weiss; phone: (888) 346-9867.
</P>
<P>
   INTERNATIONAL
</P>
