doubles. By Robin Finn.
</P>
<P>
   TONY-AWARDS (New York) _ The Tony Awards. Broadcast begins at 8
p.m. ET on PBS, and 9 p.m. ET on CBS. By Robin Pogrebin. (Photo
reefer.)
</P>
<P>
   MORGANSTANLEY-CURRY (Undated) _ A Special Report: A look at
Christian Curry, the man at the center of the discrimination suit
against Morgan Stanley Dean Witter. By Joseph Kahn.
</P>
</TEXT>
