<HEADLINE>


</HEADLINE>
  The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following sports
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs of
June 7 and thereafter. For questions about stories, resends or
inquiries, call Eddie Ibardolasa at (818) 713-3602. 
 
 
BBN-DODGERS-ANGELS (Los Angeles) _ The Anaheim Angels face the Los
Angeles Dodgers at 1:05 PDT. 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBN-DODGERNOTES (Los Angeles) _ Dodgers notebook. 
By Matt McHale. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELS (Los Angeles) _ Angels sidebar from game at Dodger
Stadium. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BBA-ANGELNOTES (Los Angeles) _ Angels notebook. 
By Joe Haakenson/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
RAC-BELMONT (Elmont, N.Y.) _ Follow-up on the Belmont and
Charismatic. 
By Kevin Modesti. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
SOC-GALAXY-WIZARDS (Pasadena, Calif.) _ The Los Angeles Galaxy
faces the Kansas City Wizards at 12:30 p.m. PDT. 
By Fred J. Robledo/San Gabriel Valley Tribune. (Will move on the
``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-OFFBEAT (Los Angeles) _ Offbeat look at sports news this past
week. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BOX-BOXING-COLUMN (Los Angeles) _ Weekly boxing column. 
By Michael Rosenthal. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-GLANCE (Los Angeles) _ A look at sports news from Los Angeles'
past. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
GEN-TV (Los Angeles) _ TV sports highlights this week. 
By Tom Hoffarth. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 

