<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-06 23:21 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5286 &Cx1f; tib-z
u k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SAFIRE-COLUMN-1STLD-W     06-06 0769
