<HEADLINE>
DODGERS' WEEKEND TURNS SOUR
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By MATT McHALE  
 c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ Under a harsh spotlight all season, the Los
Angeles Dodgers looked up at the glare of the Sunday sun and wilted
again.
</P>
<P>
   They had a chance to sweep the crosstown Anaheim Angels at the
